1. Install driver gsm modem
2. Download and install python 2.7
  - install module pyserial
  - install module python-gsmmodem
3. Download source Web2py from web2py.com http://www.web2py.com/examples/static/web2py_src.zip
  - Extract web2py_src.zip to C:\web2py
  - Download and extract app sms and copy folder sms to C:\web2py\applications\
    https://www.dropbox.com/s/rnxnqzx55acqf4l/sms.zip
4. Run the web2py
  - copy file run.bat to C:\web2py
  - click run.bat
  - connect to http://your_hostame/admin and edit/update database email add/phone number
  - edit your zimbra hostname and zimbra user C:\web2py\applications\sms\private\sms.py
-------------------------------------
NOW you login to zimbra user and send email to another email and cc or bcc to sms
